      class  btDiscreteDynamicsWorldMt
      btDiscreteDynamicsWorldMt -- a version of DiscreteDynamicsWorld with some minor changes to support solving simulation islands on multiple threads.

      The btMultiBodyDynamicsWorld adds Featherstone multi body dynamics to Bullet This implementation is still preliminary/experimental.
      class  btSimpleDynamicsWorld
      The btSimpleDynamicsWorld serves as unit-test and to verify more complicated and optimized dynamics worlds.
